org.shared.parallel

Class Engine.ThrowableReferenceHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicReference<Throwable>
      • org.shared.parallel.Engine.ThrowableReferenceHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Thread.UncaughtExceptionHandler
    Enclosing class:
    Engine<T>

    protected static class Engine.ThrowableReferenceHandler
extends AtomicReference<Throwable>
implements Thread.UncaughtExceptionHandler
    A subclass of AtomicReference that doubles as an Thread.UncaughtExceptionHandler. It is set whenever an uncaught Throwable occurs.
